Well, so...

08:40.020 --> 08:42.940
Well,
it's just so, so...

08:43.106 --> 08:45.400
That's freaky-lookin', okay?
That's what it is.

08:45.567 --> 08:47.402
- Terkina!
- Well, it is!

08:47.528 --> 08:51.198
- I mean, what the heck is it anyway?
- He's a baby.

08:51.365 --> 08:54.785
Ow! I can't...

08:56.245 --> 08:59.540
So, where's his mama?

08:59.706 --> 09:02.918
Well, I'm going to be
his mother now.

09:07.714 --> 09:11.426
You know, he's not so bad
once you get used to him.

09:12.386 --> 09:15.472
Kala's gonna be its mother now.

09:19.601 --> 09:23.522
Kerchak, I saved him from Sabor.

09:26.275 --> 09:29.403
Kala, it won't replace
the one we lost.

09:29.570 --> 09:33.407
I know that.
But... he needs me.

09:33.574 --> 09:38.245
But, it-it-it...
Kala, look at it.

09:38.412 --> 09:40.622
It's not our kind.

09:40.789 --> 09:44.585
No. You have to take it back.

09:44.710 --> 09:47.462
Take him back?
But he'll die!

09:47.629 --> 09:49.756
- If the jungle wants him...
- I want him.

09:49.923 --> 09:52.134
Kala, I cannot let you put
our family in danger.

09:52.301 --> 09:54.970
Does he look dangerous to you?

10:02.561 --> 10:05.898
Hmm. Was it alone?

10:06.064 --> 10:08.400
Yes.
Sabor killed his family.

10:08.567 --> 10:12.571
- Are you sure?
- Yes. There are no others.

10:15.240 --> 10:16.867
Then you may keep him.

10:19.077 --> 10:22.456
- Kerchak, I know he'll be a good son.
- I said he could stay.

10:23.540 --> 10:25.417
That doesn't make him
my son.

10:27.127 --> 10:30.672
We will nest here
for the night.

10:35.928 --> 10:38.597
So, um,
whatcha gonna call it?

10:38.764 --> 10:42.476
I'm gonna call him...
Tarzan.

10:42.643 --> 10:46.188
Tarzan? Okay.
He's your baby.

10:46.355 --> 10:49.483
All right, little lady, come on.
It's way past your nest time.

10:49.650 --> 10:51.527
- Oh, Mom, five more minutes?
- No!

10:51.693 --> 10:53.862
- Two more minutes?
- No!

10:54.029 --> 10:56.698
One more "minutes"?

11:00.702 --> 11:02.454
Oh, no, no, no.

11:02.579 --> 11:06.166
Shh, shh, shh. Don't cry. I'm here.

11:06.333 --> 11:08.836
Come on, come on.

11:09.002 --> 11:13.507
<i>Come, stop your crying
It'll be all right</i>

11:14.550 --> 11:18.804
