You seem so strong</i>

11:34.152 --> 11:38.156
<i>My arms will hold you
Keep you safe and warm</i>

11:38.323 --> 11:43.787
<i>This bond between us
can't be broken</i>

11:43.954 --> 11:47.875
<i>I will be here
Don't you cry</i>

11:48.041 --> 11:52.546
<i>'Cause you'll be in my heart</i>

11:52.713 --> 11:56.633
<i>Yes, you'll be in my heart</i>

11:57.759 --> 12:03.473
<i>From this day on
Now and forever more</i>

12:07.603 --> 12:11.857
<i>You'll be in my heart</i>

12:12.024 --> 12:16.695
<i>No matter what they say</i>

12:16.862 --> 12:21.408
<i>You'll be here in my heart</i>

12:21.575 --> 12:24.119
<i>Always</i>

