come up with your own sound?

13:22.719 --> 13:24.429
Kala!

13:28.892 --> 13:31.937
Oops.

13:32.104 --> 13:33.939
Hee-hee.

13:34.106 --> 13:36.441
Tarzan, thank goodness
you're all right!

13:36.608 --> 13:40.320
Kala and I have been
so worried!

13:40.487 --> 13:43.740
Thank you. Thank you so much
for finding him, Kerchak.

13:43.907 --> 13:46.285
You are such a wise
and caring leader.

13:46.451 --> 13:48.495
Run.

13:48.662 --> 13:50.956
Ooh!
Um...

13:53.876 --> 13:56.461
- Hello! Are you thick in the head?
- What?

13:56.545 --> 13:58.297
How many times
do I have to tell ya?

13:58.380 --> 14:02.092
If you want Kerchak to like you,
stay away from him!

14:02.176 --> 14:04.469
- Come on, Terk! Step on it!
- Last one there's a dung beetle!

14:04.636 --> 14:08.265
- Yeah! And the first one's gotta eat it!
- Terk, can I come?

14:08.432 --> 14:12.561
Well, yeah, you could if you could keep
up, but... you can't really keep up.

14:12.728 --> 14:16.732
Wait up, guys.
Wait up! Right behind ya.

14:25.616 --> 14:28.285
Ah, yeah, take that.
Stop hitting yourself.

14:28.452 --> 14:32.247
Stop hitting yourself!
Stop hitting yourself!

14:32.414 --> 14:36.293
<i>The fun has arrived</i>
Thank you very much.

14:36.460 --> 14:37.961
What took you
so long?

14:38.128 --> 14:42.674
I had a little pest control problem,
but it's all taken care of.

14:43.592 --> 14:45.010
Hi, guys.

14:45.177 --> 14:48.263
Terk, what is this?
Some kind of joke?

14:48.430 --> 14:50.807
Tell me I'm not lookin'
at the hairless wonder.

14:50.974 --> 14:53.769
Terk said I could come along
if I could keep up.

14:55.312 --> 14:57.523
- Ah, no, Terk, come on!
- Terk!

14:57.606 --> 15:00.108
I'll handle this, guys.
Okay?

15:00.275 --> 15:01.818
Listen, buddy, come here.

15:02.027 --> 15:04.655
We got a tiny,
little, itsy-bitsy problem here.

15:04.738 --> 15:07.574
Personally, I'd love to hang out
with you. You know I would.

15:07.741 --> 15:10.828
But the guys, they need
a little convincing, you know.

15:10.994 --> 15:12.538
Okay.
What do I gotta do?

15:12.704 --> 15:16.834
Do? What do you gotta do?
It's so stupid!

15:17.000 --> 15:22.798
- What?
- Well, you gotta... You gotta go get a hair.

15:22.881 --> 15:23.632
A hair?

15:23.882 --> 15:27.469
Yeah, a hair.

15:27.636 --> 15:29.888
An elephant hair.

15:34.977 --> 15:36.520
An elephant hair?

15:36.603 --> 15:39.106
Like I said,
it's stupid, right?

15:39.189 --> 15:41.733
Listen, take it from me.
Go home, okay?

15:41.900 --> 15:46.530
Who needs this aggravation? You know?
I'm probably gonna leave soon myself.

15:46.697 --> 15:49.533
You go, I'll catch up.
All right?

15:49.700 --> 15:53.537
You see? Leave it to me.
I told ya... Tarzan!

15:53.704 --> 15:55.998
Tarzan, no!

16:03.547 --> 16:06.592
That one hurt him.

16:23.734 --> 16:25.068
Look!

16:25.235 --> 16:29.239
- Oh, oh, there he is! He's alive!
- Hey, guys!

16:29.406 --> 16:31.033
Hi!

16:31.200 --> 16:34.453
Oh, no. No, no, no!

16:34.536 --> 16:37.831
Come back!
Come back!

16:37.915 --> 16:41.627
This guy's great! If he lives,
you should bring him around more often.

16:41.793 --> 16:45.088
- Come on, let's go get a better seat.
- Ohh.

16:46.548 --> 16:50.469
- You never get enough sleep.
- I get enough sleep.

16:50.636 --> 16:55.265
Mom, are you sure
this water's sanitary?

16:55.474 --> 16:58.393
It looks questionable to me.

16:58.560 --> 17:00.521
It's fine, honey.

17:00.687 --> 17:05.108
Yech!
But what about bacteria?

17:05.192 --> 17:08.612
Tantor, can't you see
Mommy's talking?

17:12.866 --> 17:17.496
Watch out! There's something
swimming! It's coming right at you!

17:17.579 --> 17:19.498
Honey, Mommy's losing
her patience.

17:19.665 --> 17:23.502
- But this time I really see something!
- Oh, boy.

17:23.585 --> 17:26.128
Piranha! It's a piranha!

17:26.296 --> 17:29.925
Sweetheart, there are
no piranhas in Africa.

17:30.008 --> 17:33.512
Don't tell the kid that. Of course
there are piranhas in Africa.

17:33.595 --> 17:36.014
No, she's right.
They're native to South America.

17:36.098 --> 17:37.683
Get outta here.

17:37.766 --> 17:41.353
No way! Come on. Do you think
I'd be standing here if...

17:41.436 --> 17:43.730
Aah! It's right behind you!
Run!

17:43.897 --> 17:48.402
For the last time, honey, there
are no piranhas in...

17:48.485 --> 17:49.945
My butt!

17:50.487 --> 17:53.365
- I told you!
- There's something on my butt.

17:53.448 --> 17:55.242
- What is it?
- Are there any more of them?

17:56.034 --> 18:00.914
- What is it?
- It's a piranha!

18:01.498 --> 18:03.208
Huh?

18:04.459 --> 18:06.712
Piranha!

18:09.131 --> 18:11.091
Tantor, where are...

18:22.019 --> 18:24.021
He's dead!

18:24.146 --> 18:26.023
We're dead!

18:32.487 --> 18:34.865
We didn't do it!
They're the ones!

18:52.758 --> 18:55.093
Oh, thank you, Kerchak.

18:58.680 --> 19:01.391
Tarzan, buddy! Buddy, come on.
Tarzan, don't die on me.

19:01.558 --> 19:04.186
Don't die on me.
You weren't supposed to do it!

19:04.269 --> 19:08.190
Get away from there! Don't you know a
piranha can strip your flesh in seconds?

19:08.273 --> 19:11.318
What? He's not a piranha!
He's...

19:12.319 --> 19:13.570
He's alive!

19:13.737 --> 19:16.782
- He's alive! He's alive!
- He's alive!

19:16.949 --> 19:19.618
He's alive...
You idiot!

19:19.785 --> 19:23.455
You nearly gave me a heart
attack. Ya happy?

19:23.580 --> 19:27.251
You... I don't believe it.
You got the hair?

19:27.417 --> 19:32.005
Is that what this is all about?
I got a whole tail of them.

19:32.965 --> 19:34.007
- Tarzan!
- Terkina!

19:34.424 --> 19:35.592
Oh, no!

19:36.385 --> 19:38.428
- Who's that?
- My mom.

19:38.595 --> 19:41.557
- Tarzan!
- Hi, Aunt Kala.

19:41.723 --> 19:44.643
- Oh, you scared me! What happened?
- Well, I...

19:44.726 --> 19:48.605
It's sort of a long...
It's involved because what happened...

19:48.689 --> 19:50.774
- It was a weird...
- What happened?

19:53.402 --> 19:56.572
- It was my fault, Kerchak.
- Tarzan!

19:56.738 --> 20:01.410
We were playing and well...
I'm... I'm sorry, Kerchak.

20:01.577 --> 20:03.579
You almost killed someone!

20:03.745 --> 20:05.789
- But it was an accident.
- He's only a child.

20:05.956 --> 20:08.417
That's no excuse, Kala!
You can't keep defending him!

20:08.500 --> 20:09.960
- But he'll learn!
- He will never learn!

20:10.127 --> 20:13.213
- You can't learn to be one of us.
- Because you never give him a chance!

20:13.297 --> 20:18.594
Give him a chance? Kala, look at him.
He will never be one of us.

20:18.760 --> 20:20.846
Kerchak!

20:21.013 --> 20:23.265
Tarzan!

21:13.524 --> 21:15.817
Tarzan,
what are you doing?

21:16.485 --> 21:18.487
Why am I so different?

21:18.654 --> 21:20.697
Because you're covered
with mud. That's why.

21:20.864 --> 21:24.660
- No! Kerchak said I didn't
belong in the... - Close your mouth.

21:24.743 --> 21:26.245
Said I don't belong
in the family.

21:26.411 --> 21:29.748
Never mind what Kerchak said.
Now, hold still!

21:29.915 --> 21:31.750
But, look at me!

21:34.336 --> 21:38.257
I am, Tarzan.
And do you know what I see?

21:38.423 --> 21:41.426
I see two eyes,
like mine.

21:41.593 --> 21:44.930
And a nose...
somewhere.

21:45.097 --> 21:47.766
Ahh... here!

21:47.891 --> 21:50.394
Two ears!

21:51.103 --> 21:53.772
- And, let's see. What else?
- Two hands?

21:53.939 --> 21:55.774
That's right.

22:12.082 --> 22:14.376
Close your eyes.

22:14.543 --> 22:18.755
Now forget what you see.
What do you feel?

22:20.465 --> 22:21.550
My heart.

22:22.134 --> 22:23.218
Come here.

22:24.970 --> 22:27.306
- Your heart.
- See?

22:27.472 --> 22:31.351
We're exactly the same.

22:31.518 --> 22:35.189
Oh!
Kerchak just can't see that.

22:37.733 --> 22:39.234
I'll make him see it!

22:39.484 --> 22:41.653
I'll be the best ape ever!

22:41.820 --> 22:45.282
Oh, I bet you will.

22:57.920 --> 23:01.548
<i>Oh, the power to be strong</i>

23:01.715 --> 23:05.427
<i>And the wisdom
to be wise</i>

23:05.594 --> 23:10.182
<i>All these things
will come to you in time</i>

23:11.475 --> 23:14.728
<i>On this journey
that you're making</i>

23:14.895 --> 23:18.190
