24:27.134 --> 24:29.136
<i>In learning
you will teach</i>

24:29.303 --> 24:33.182
<i>And in teaching
you will learn</i>

24:33.348 --> 24:37.895
<i>You'll find your place
beside the ones you love</i>

24:39.354 --> 24:43.567
<i>All and all
the things you've dreamed of</i>

24:43.734 --> 24:46.653
<i>The visions that you saw</i>

24:46.820 --> 24:50.073
<i>Well, the time
is drawing near now</i>

24:50.240 --> 24:53.702
<i>It's yours to claim it all</i>

